on Music Chart|accessdate=June 20, 2019|language=ko}}\n</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"|[[K-pop Hot 100|KOR<br>Hot]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/everglow/chart-history/KPO|title=Everglow Chart History: Billboard Korea K-Pop 100|website=Billboard|access-date=April 9, 2020}}\n</ref>\n! scope= \"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Billboard Japan Hot 100|JPN<br/>Hot]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/everglow/chart-history/JPN|title=Everglow Chart History: Japan Hot 100|website=Billboard|access-date=February 26, 2020}}\n</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"|[[Billboard charts#International charts|US<br>World]]<br><ref name=\"wdt\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/everglow/chart-history/WDT|title=Everglow Chart History: World Digital Song Sales|website=Billboard|access-date=February 26, 2020}}\n</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Bon Bon Chocolat\" {{small|{{lang|ko|(\ubd09\ubd09\uc1fc\ucf5c\ub77c)}}}}\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2019\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 5\n|\n* US: 5,000<ref name=\"adios\">{{cite web|title=EVERGLOW Hit New Peak on World Digital Song Sales Chart With Three Songs In Top 10|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/8528761/everglow-adios-new-peak-world-digital-song-sales-chart|website=Billboard|accessdate=August 30, 2019|language=en}}</ref>\n| ''Arrival of Everglow''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Adios\"\n| \u2014 || 74 || \u2014 || 2\n|\n* US: 1,000<ref name=\"adios\"/>\n|''Hush''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Dun Dun\"\n| 2020\n| \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Dun Dun\" did not enter the Gaon Digital Chart, but appeared at number 63 on the component Download chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S1020&targetTime=06&hitYear=2020&termGbn=week|script-title=ko:2020\ub144 06\uc8fc\ucc28 Download Chart|trans-title=Week 6 of 2020 Download Chart|date=February 2\u20138, 202